cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.SD

This paper is about a challenge related to social multimedia data and prediction tasks. The most relevant sub-category is cs.MM (Multimedia), which deals with the processing, analysis, and understanding of multimedia data. The paper also mentions the use of advanced predictive learning and analytic methods, which suggests the involvement of sub-categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The challenge also involves evaluating the accuracy and correlation of predictions, which could fall under sub-categories such as cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SD (Software Engineering).
